          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="x_content">
          <p>This is a form help you track where are your products. To help you know your products come to customers or not.</p>
          <p>Order Items have 3 status: Preparing -> Transporting -> Transported. When all products in 1 ORDER is "Transported". This order is ready to delivery. If not, it still was pending.</p>
          <div id="wizard" class="form_wizard wizard_horizontal">
            <ul class="wizard_steps">
              <li>
                <a href="#step-1">
                  <span class="step_no">1</span>
                  <span class="step_descr">
                      Pending<br />
                  </span>
                </a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a href="#step-2">
                  <span class="step_no">2</span>
